{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you couldn't-- they-- they were very-- see, they-- the Germans, managed to-- to perform this, to do this-- this-- this 'Final Solution,' so to say, was decided, in '42, in Wannsee, I remember.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was already in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then they decided the 'Final Solution' of the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before that, they had, more or less, constantly to-- to-- to evacuate them from Berlin and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were no witnesses, no signs of this cruel situation, which was going to happen later on, about Auschwitz and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That we didn't learn till-- till-- really, we didn't get any authentic reports on that till-- till I came to-- to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left Berlin in 1941, in the summer, the day when the-- when the-- the Germans invaded the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not in Berlin, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't-- we weren't involved in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that the-- the Swedish Church and all that were trying to help the Jews in a-- on a small, very small scale at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it hadn't-- it wasn't very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't-- it wasn't possible to observe anything, because everything-- everything was so done in a-- in a-- in a very clever way by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They slowly evacuate the-- the Jews from-- f from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This-- there were rumors that they-- you put them into the camps, because they-- the-- the Germans didn't want them to be on the-- on the battlefield and all that and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the first reports we got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not from Berlin, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- It was too early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The stage was too early.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was absorbed by my job, by the commercial negotiations and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
